These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, almond-milk, fanta
Pet: turtle, pony, rat, rabbit
1. Pet:rabbit is on the left of Beverage:almond-milk##1
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Pet:pony##1
3. Beverage:fanta is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:rat is on the left or right of Pet:rabbit##3
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | fanta | almond-milk |
| Pet        | turtle | pony   | rabbit | rat    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: epic, drama, animation, documentary
Nationality: malaysian, australian, chinese, pakistani
1. Movie-Genre:drama is on the left of Movie-Genre:documentary##1
2. Nationality:malaysian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
3. Nationality:chinese is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:malaysian == Movie-Genre:epic##1
5. Nationality:australian is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
6. Nationality:malaysian == Movie-Genre:epic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | epic  | drama  | documentary |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | malaysian | chinese | australian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: pineapple, pumpkin, lime, avocado
Movie-Genre: adventure, mystery, superhero, martial-arts
1. Food:avocado is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:martial-arts##3
2. Food:lime is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the left or right of Food:pumpkin##3
4. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the right of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
5. Movie-Genre:adventure is in an odd position##4
6. Food:pumpkin is on the right of Food:lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | avocado | lime | pumpkin    | pineapple      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | martial-arts     | adventure | mystery |

