.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: puzzles, writing, photography, collecting
Music-Genre: electronic, classical, gospel, ambient
1. Hobby:writing is between Music-Genre:electronic and Music-Genre:ambient##2
2. Hobby:collecting is on the left of Hobby:puzzles##1
3. Music-Genre:gospel is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:classical is on the left of Music-Genre:ambient##1
5. Music-Genre:classical is on the right of Hobby:puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | collecting | puzzles | writing | photography |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | electronic   | classical    | ambient  |

