.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: rock, metal, soul, trance
Nationality: dutch, nigerian, chinese, pakistani
1. Music-Genre:soul is on the right of Nationality:pakistani##1
2. Nationality:nigerian == Music-Genre:trance##1
3. Nationality:chinese is on the right of Music-Genre:rock##1
4. Music-Genre:metal is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:soul is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:dutch is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | rock    | soul   | trance       |
| Nationality   | dutch | pakistani | chinese | nigerian |

