.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: milk, iced-tea, tea, coffee
Music-Genre: techno, trance, funk, metal
1. Beverage:milk == Music-Genre:metal##1
2. Music-Genre:techno is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
3. Music-Genre:metal is between Music-Genre:techno and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:metal is on the left or right of Music-Genre:techno##3
6. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | tea   | milk | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | funk | trance | metal        | techno    |

