.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, juice, cola, almond-milk
Food: almond-milkmelon, broccoli, papaya, asparagus
1. Food:broccoli is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##3
3. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:papaya is on the left of Food:asparagus##1
5. Food:asparagus is on the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
6. Food:papaya is in an even position##4
7. Food:almond-milkmelon == Beverage:juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate    | cola       | juice |
| Food       | broccoli  | papaya | asparagus | almond-milkmelon  |

